<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Evaluación Viajeros</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/index.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/ionicons.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/animate.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/nice-select.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/owl.carousel.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mainmenu.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-select@1.13.9/dist/css/bootstrap-select.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap-datepicker.standalone.css" />
    <script src="/js/vendor/modernizr-2.8.3.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lozad/dist/lozad.min.js"></script>		
</head>

<body>
    {{!-- Barra superior --}}
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg" style="justify-content: space-between; max-width:90em;">
        <a href="https://www.cdmadero.tecnm.mx/">
            <img src="/img/itcm.png" class="logo"> 
        </a>
        <a href="">
            <img src="/img/itcm.png" class="logo"> 
        </a>
    </nav>

    <div class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">
                <div class="">
                    <div class="">
                        <h2 class="">Evaluación viajeros</h2>
                        <h2>COVID-19</h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">
                <div class="container">
                    <h4>Iniciar Sesión</h4>
                    <p>¡Bienvenido de nuevo! Por favor, introduzca sus datos.</p>

                    <form id="form_login">
                        <p class="coupon-input form-row-last">
							<label>Email</label>
							<input id="input_correo" name="input_correo" type="text" autocomplete="off">
						</p>
                        <p class="coupon-input form-row-last">
							<label>Contraseña</label>
							<input id="input_password" name="input_password" maxlength="15" type="password" autocomplete="off">
						</p>
                        <button onclick="iniciar_sesion()" type="button">Inicia Sesión</button>
                    </form>

                    <p>¿Todavía no tienes cuenta? 
                        <button type="button" id="btnexampleModal" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal"
                        style="border: none; background: none;"
                        >
                            <strong>Regístrate</strong>
                        </button >
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{!-- Barra inferior --}}
    <nav class="navbar fixed-bottom navbar-expand-lg navbar-light" >
        <div class="container-fluid">
           <p>Copyright ©. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Modal para registro de administrador -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h4 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Regístrate para iniciar</h4>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form id="form_registro">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Nombre(s)</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="nombre" id="nombre">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Apellido paterno</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="paterno" id="paterno">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Apellido Materno</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="materno" id="materno">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col">
                             <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="correo" id="correo">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <label class="form-label">Contraseña</label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" name="contrasena" id="contrasena">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col">
                      <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="registrar_usuario()">Registrar</button>  
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{>script}}
</body>

</html>